---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kids @The Life Place">
  <section class="container-x py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-6">Kids @The Life Place</h1>

    <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-orange-200">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Kids Ministry</h3>
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white">
          Coming Soon
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We don’t yet have a children’s ministry. As Jesus provides people and resources, we will begin one where our children too will
        <em> Come. See. Jesus.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>